{"word":"G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee' - Am","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰμί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eimí</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">i-mee'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Am</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இரு"},{"paragraph":"to be, to exist"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>First person singular present indicative; a prolonged form of a primary and defective verb; I <i>exist</i> (used only when emphatic): - am, have been, X it is I, was. See also <a href=\"#/G1488 - εἶ - eî - i/1488\">G1488</a>, <a href=\"#/G1498 - εἴην - eíēn - i'-ane/1498\">G1498</a>, <a href=\"#/G1511 - εἶναι - eînai - i'-nahee/1511\">G1511</a>, <a href=\"#/G1527 - εἷς καθ’ εἷς - heîs kath’ heîs - hice kath hice/1527\">G1527</a>, <a href=\"#/G2258 - ἦν - ēn - ane/2258\">G2258</a>, <a href=\"#/G2071 - ἔσομαι - ésomai - es'-om-ahee/2071\">G2071</a>, <a href=\"#/G2070 - ἐσμέν - esmén - es-men'/2070\">G2070</a>, <a href=\"#/G2075 - ἐστέ - esté - es-teh'/2075\">G2075</a>, <a href=\"#/G2076 - ἐστί - estí - es-tee'/2076\">G2076</a>, <a href=\"#/G2771 - κέρδος - kérdos - ker'-dos/2771\">G2771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2468 - ἴσθι - ísthi - is'-thee/2468\">G2468</a>, <a href=\"#/G5600 - ὦ - ō - o/5600\">G5600</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1510/1510\">G1510</a>, <a href=\"#/G5607/5607\">G5607</a>"}]}